task.summary: Cross datacenter database :) Only workloads that span multiple datacenters are replicated across datacenters.

Single datacenter optimized transactions.
Future implementation for multidatacenter solutions:
- Log: only use global consensus between datacenters involved. This is an optimization for low latency local epochs (those that don't envolve multiple datacenters) - Execution: local epochs can execute right away. When processing a global epoch => ask involved dcs whether they are in the same global epoch. Only process the global epoch when all dcs are ready to proceed.
Single DC implementation for distributed transactions.
